<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Profile Status Update</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header.approved {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #138808 0%, #27ae60 100%);
        }
        
        .header.rejected {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%);
        }
        
        .header.suspended {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12 0%, #e67e22 100%);
        }
        
        .header.pending {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db 0%, #2980b9 100%);
        }
        
        .status-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .status-box {
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .status-box.approved {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4edda 0%, #c3e6cb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #138808;
        }
        
        .status-box.rejected {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8d7da 0%, #f5c6cb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #e74c3c;
        }
        
        .status-box.suspended {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd 0%, #ffeaa7 100%);
            border: 2px solid #f39c12;
        }
        
        .status-box.pending {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #cce7ff 0%, #b3d9ff 100%);
            border: 2px solid #3498db;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .status-badge.approved {
            background: #138808;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .status-badge.rejected {
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .status-badge.suspended {
            background: #f39c12;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .status-badge.pending {
            background: #3498db;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .message-section {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .reason-section {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #6c757d;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .reason-section h4 {
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .reason-section p {
            color: #6c757d;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .next-steps.approved {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            border-left: 4px solid #138808;
        }
        
        .next-steps.rejected {
            background: #ffebee;
            border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
        }
        
        .next-steps.suspended {
            background: #fff8e1;
            border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
        }
        
        .next-steps.pending {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .next-steps.approved h3 {
            color: #138808;
        }
        
        .next-steps.rejected h3 {
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        
        .next-steps.suspended h3 {
            color: #f39c12;
        }
        
        .next-steps.pending h3 {
            color: #3498db;
        }
        
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            counter-reset: step-counter;
        }
        
        .steps-list li {
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            padding: 10px 0;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 40px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .steps-list li:before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 10px;
            width: 25px;
            height: 25px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .next-steps.approved .steps-list li:before {
            background: #138808;
        }
        
        .next-steps.rejected .steps-list li:before {
            background: #e74c3c;
        }
        
        .next-steps.suspended .steps-list li:before {
            background: #f39c12;
        }
        
        .next-steps.pending .steps-list li:before {
            background: #3498db;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin: 10px;
        }
        
        .cta-button.approved {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #138808 0%, #27ae60 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-button.primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db 0%, #2980b9 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header {{newStatus}}">
            <div class="status-icon">
                {{#if (eq newStatus 'approved')}}‚úÖ{{/if}}
                {{#if (eq newStatus 'rejected')}}‚ùå{{/if}}
                {{#if (eq newStatus 'suspended')}}‚ö†Ô∏è{{/if}}
                {{#if (eq newStatus 'pending')}}‚è≥{{/if}}
            </div>
            <h1>Profile Status Update</h1>
            <p>Your account status has been updated</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                Hi {{firstName}},
            </p>
            
            <div class="status-box {{newStatus}}">
                <div class="status-badge {{newStatus}}">{{newStatus}}</div>
                <h2 style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'approved')}}Congratulations! Your profile has been approved{{/if}}
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'rejected')}}Profile Review Update{{/if}}
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'suspended')}}Profile Temporarily Suspended{{/if}}
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'pending')}}Profile Under Review{{/if}}
                </h2>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px;">
                    {{statusMessage}}
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message-section">
                <h3 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 15px;">Status Details</h3>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'approved')}}
                    Your profile has been reviewed and approved. You now have full access to all platform features and benefits.
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'rejected')}}
                    After careful review, we were unable to approve your profile at this time. Please review the reason below and consider resubmitting with the necessary corrections.
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'suspended')}}
                    Your profile has been temporarily suspended. This may be due to policy violations or account security concerns.
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'pending')}}
                    Your profile is currently under review by our team. We'll notify you once the review is complete.
                    {{/if}}
                </p>
                
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps {{newStatus}}">
                <h3>
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'approved')}}üéâ Next Steps{{/if}}
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'rejected')}}üìù What You Can Do{{/if}}
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'suspended')}}üîÑ Resolution Steps{{/if}}
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'pending')}}‚è±Ô∏è What Happens Next{{/if}}
                </h3>
                
                <ol class="steps-list">
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'approved')}}
                    <li>Log into your account to access all features</li>
                    <li>Complete your profile if you haven't already</li>
                    <li>Start browsing and redeeming exclusive deals</li>
                    <li>Connect with the Indian community in Ghana</li>
                    <li>Explore upcoming events and activities</li>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'rejected')}}
                    <li>Update your profile with correct information</li>
                    <li>Ensure all required documents are provided</li>
                    <li>Resubmit your profile for review</li>
                    <li>Contact support if you need assistance</li>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'suspended')}}
                    <li>Review our terms and conditions</li>
                    <li>Contact support to understand the suspension</li>
                    <li>Take necessary corrective actions</li>
                    <li>Submit an appeal if appropriate</li>
                    <li>Wait for resolution from our team</li>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    {{#if (eq newStatus 'pending')}}
                    <li>Your profile is in our review queue</li>
                    <li>We'll review within 24-48 hours</li>
                    <li>You'll receive email notification once complete</li>
                    <li>No action required from your side</li>
                    <li>Feel free to contact us with questions</li>
                    {{/if}}
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                {{#if (eq newStatus 'approved')}}
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-button approved">Access Your Account</a>
                {{else}}
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-button primary">Log In to Account</a>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center;">
                <h4 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 15px;">Need Help?</h4>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    Our support team is here to assist you with any questions or concerns.
                </p>
                <p style="color: #666;">
                    üìß Email: support@indiansinghana.com<br>
                    üì± WhatsApp: +233 XXX XXX XXX<br>
                    üïí Support Hours: Monday - Friday, 9 AM - 6 PM (GMT)
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana</strong> - Connecting Community, Creating Value</p>
            <p>This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
            <p>Email: {{supportEmail}} | Website: www.indiansinghana.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
